<https://w3id.org/mdivo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://w3id.org/mdivo> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionIRI> <https://w3id.org/mdivo/1.0> .
<https://w3id.org/mdivo> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> "Nil Arilla"@en .
<https://w3id.org/mdivo> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> "https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/" .
<https://w3id.org/mdivo> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "MDIVO Ontology"@en .
<https://w3id.org/mdivo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ontology for the European catalogue of high risk medical devices and in-vitro diagnostic devices, aligned with EU Regulations MDR (2017/745) and IVDR (2017/746) and the EUDAMED database."@en .
<https://w3id.org/mdivo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Medical Devices and In-Vitro Diagnostics Ontology (MDIVO)"@en .
